WEBVTT

00:06:59.672 --> 00:07:03.613
you have to hide or push down
the feelings you're actually having,

00:07:03.637 --> 00:07:05.966
and just get through that situation.

00:07:05.990 --> 00:07:10.386
The problem is when you're engaging
in that surface acting repeatedly.

00:07:10.784 --> 00:07:15.760
Doing it one time with your
aunt Bernadette might not be a big deal.

00:07:15.784 --> 00:07:20.702
But doing it constantly with customers
over and over again,

00:07:20.726 --> 00:07:23.739
because you're always dealing
with customers who are upset

00:07:23.763 --> 00:07:25.621
or patients who are upset ...

00:07:25.645 --> 00:07:29.246
Having to do that constantly
is where we see the problem.